The paper discusses a distributed infrastructure for training graph embeddings at scale, which involves machine learning and distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also mentions link prediction and recommendation, which are common applications in information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI), respectively.
